#### Example Usage

```typescript
import * as pulumi from "@pulumi/pulumi";

const recordsDs = pulumi.all([alicloud_pvtz_zone_record_foo.value, alicloud_pvtz_zone_basic.id]).apply(([value, id]) => alicloud.pvtz.getZoneRecords({

    zoneId: id,
}, { async: true }));

```
